<p>Dreaming of getting out on the slopes this winter? Don't miss out on great value when you book your European ski holiday for 2024/25 and 2025/26 with our lift pass and ski equipment offer.</p>
<p>Simply add this offer to your booking in the ski extras section during the booking process – just pick your lift pass and the discount on the equipment will be applied automatically if you’re eligible for it.</p>
